    h3 2-INPUT NAND GATE IC-7400
    p IC-7400(Fig-14) designates a device containing four input NAND gates. Each gate uses two pins for input and one pin for its output, and the remaining two contacts are connected to supply power (+5 V) and the ground.
    h3 3-INPUT NAND GATE IC-7410
    p IC-7410 (Fig-15) is a Triple 3-input NAND gate and contains three independent gates each of which performs logic NAND operation
    .row 
